      "widgets_values": [
        "Advanced LTX-Video Workflow v2.0.2\n\n\ud83d\udd27 Complete Modular Pipeline (All Nodes Connected)\n\nWorkflow Flow:\n1. Prompt Enhancer \u2192 Enhances your prompt\n2. Full Pipeline \u2192 Generates base video\n3. Frame Interpolator \u2192 Extends duration\n4. Upscaler \u2192 Increases resolution to 4K\n5. Video Combine \u2192 Final MP4 output\n\nNode Details:\n\n1\ufe0f\u20e3 Prompt Enhancer:\n   - Automatically enhances basic prompts\n   - Enhancement levels: Minimal/Moderate/Maximum\n   - Style presets: Realistic/Cinematic/Artistic\n   - Adds temporal consistency keywords\n\n2\ufe0f\u20e3 Full Pipeline:\n   - Main generation node with all controls\n   - 'Detailed' mode for pre-enhanced prompts\n   - 10s duration for longer clips\n   - Higher steps (80+) for maximum quality\n   - Model auto-loads from HuggingFace\n\n3\ufe0f\u20e3 Frame Interpolator:\n   - Extends video duration smoothly\n   - 25 FPS target for smooth playback\n   - Maintains temporal consistency\n   - Linear interpolation (upgradeable to RIFE)\n\n4\ufe0f\u20e3 Upscaler:\n   - 4K upscaling with 2x scale factor\n   - Tiled processing for VRAM efficiency\n   - Bicubic interpolation (upgradeable to ESRGAN)\n   - Handles large frames efficiently\n\n5\ufe0f\u20e3 Video Output:\n   - Combines frames into H.264 MP4\n   - CRF 18 for high quality (lower = better)\n   - 25 FPS matches interpolator\n   - Metadata embedded automatically\n\n\u2705 All nodes connected - Drag, drop, and run!\n\ud83d\udcc5 Updated: November 2024"
